            "reviews": "“The game manages to get over some of the hurdles of the game books quite neatly. So if this is your first trip into the classic universe, you'll probably have a damn good time.”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/iPhone/Fighting+Fantasy+Legends/review.asp?c=74821\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >PocketGamer</a><br><br>“Fans of the series will love having a different way of approaching some of their favorite characters. It’s an entertaining twist on the usual Choose Your Own Adventure format.”<br>4/5 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.gamezebo.com/2017/08/03/fighting-fantasy-legends-review-dice-fate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >GameZebo</a><br>",
